Harrison Ford (silent film actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harrison_Ford_(silent_film_actor) 0 Harrison Edward Ford (March 16, 1884 – December 2, 1957) was an American stage and film actor. He was a leading Broadway theatre performer and a star of the silent film era. Harrison_Edward_Ford ( March_16_,_1884 – December_2_,_1957 ) was an_American_stage_and_film_actor .
